<h2>You've been invited to {{app_name}}</h2>
<p>Hello,</p>
<p>You have been invited to join <strong>{{app_name}}</strong>.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="{{invite_url}}" class="button">
        Accept Invitation
    </a>
</p>
<p style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9em;">
    This invitation will expire on <strong>{{expires_str}}</strong>.
</p>
<div class="alert-info">
    You will need to login with your <strong>Google account</strong> to complete the registration.
</div>
<hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 20px 0;">
<p style="color: #999; font-size: 0.8em;">
    If you did not expect this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.
</p>
